fields.Title: BOARDWALK / RAILING
fields.Description: You've discovered Idiot Doom Spiral's missing jacket.

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "A poet could write a dozen verses a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A poet could write a dozen verses and still not begin to capture the profound vexation in that sigh.

fields.Title: You: ""It could have been multiple seagul..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It could have been multiple seagulls."

fields.Title: You: ""No.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Me neither.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Me neither."

fields.Title: Logic: "It seems likely that it was left in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It seems likely that it was left in the surf until someone laid it out on this fence to dry out. Unfortunately that just seems to have stiffened it into a shapeless mass.

fields.Title: You: ""It might be a clue.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It might be a clue."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A clue? You think our suspect is a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A clue? You think our suspect is a seagull who's been defecating on unsuspecting jackets?"

fields.Title: You: "Take a closer look."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take a closer look.

fields.Title: Railing: "Someone has left an unidentifiable..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Someone has left an unidentifiable article of clothing on this railing. It smells really bad.

fields.Title: You: "Touch it."
fields.Dialogue Text: Touch it.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You should still take it."
fields.Dialogue Text: You should still take it.

fields.Title: You: "Maybe later. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe later. [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""Why not?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why not?"

fields.Title: You: ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Railing: "The cloth, if you can still call it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The cloth, if you can still call it that, makes a soft crunching sound as you thrust your finger into it.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You should still take it. It's prob..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You should still take it. It's probably Doom Spiral's.

fields.Title: You: ""I think this is the jacket the Idi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think this is the jacket the Idiot Doom Spiral Guy wanted me to find."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Please tell me you're not taking t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Please tell me you're not taking that with you."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant sighs."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant sighs.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Much as the thought of touching it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Much as the thought of touching it causes you to cringe, this could be the jacket that the idiot in the colourful tracksuit was looking for...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant looks at the stinkin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant looks at the stinking rag and sniffs. "I'm sure he'll be *thrilled* to have it returned."

fields.Title: Railing: "It's streaked with dried seagull sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's streaked with dried seagull shit and tangled with pieces of seaweed. A dangling arm suggests that there might be a jacket beneath the crust of filth.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's a guano-encrusted jacket. And..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's a guano-encrusted jacket. And you're already carrying around enough as it is."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "This jacket reeks of loss and failu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This jacket reeks of loss and failure. It could be the one that the idiot in the colourful tracksuit was looking for...
